{"_id":"s62I7YXaphNefRWq","name":"Close Combat (Combat)","permission":{"default":0,"QKfICymYNdnzinV1":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you are attacking a foe in melee, you know how to maneuver to make it more difficult for other foes to target you.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Base attack bonus +1.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: When you hit an adjacent foe with a melee attack, as long as you are adjacent to that target, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your AC against attacks from other creatures that are not adjacent to you until the beginning of your next turn.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pact Worlds","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"name":"Deadly Aim (Combat)","permission":{"default":0,"QKfICymYNdnzinV1":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your can strike your enemies’ weak points and deal more damage.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Base attack bonus +1.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: When you take the attack or full attack action with weapons (including a solarian’s solar manifestation, but not spells or other special abilities of any kind), you can take a –2 penalty to your attack rolls. If you do, those attacks deal additional damage equal to half your base attack bonus (minimum 1).</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pact Worlds","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"1P1O0BHojSINAbRg"}
{"name":"Deadly Boast","permission":{"default":0,"QKfICymYNdnzinV1":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can make an upcoming attack or effect sound so terrifying and dangerous that its targets are actually more likely to be affected by it.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Cha 19, Bluff 10 ranks.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: As a full action, you can describe in great detail how powerful and effective a specific action taken by you or an ally is going to be. You must select a specific character to boast about, and a specific weapon, item, spell, or ability to be used. Attempt a Bluff check against all foes within 60 feet of you, using the same DC you would use if attempting to demoralize them with Intimidate—roll a single check and compare the result to the DC for each target. Each target your check succeeds against takes a –1 penalty to AC and a –2 penalty to saving throws against the action you boasted about until the end of your next turn. Once you have attempted to use this ability against a creature, it is immune to your use of this feat for 24 hours. This is a sense-dependent, language-dependent ability.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Character Operation Manual","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"anDF53RV2bBeXoUI"}
